nse)</a></div></li><li class="theme-doc-sidebar-item-category theme-doc-sidebar-item-category-level-2 menu__list-item menu__list-item--collapsed"><div class="menu__list-item-collapsible"><a class="menu__link menu__link--sublist menu__link--sublist-caret" aria-expanded="false" tabindex="0" href="/XIAO_ESP32C3_Getting_Started/">XIAO ESP32C3</a></div></li><li class="theme-doc-sidebar-item-category theme-doc-sidebar-item-category-level-2 menu__list-item menu__list-item--collapsed"><div class="menu__list-item-collapsible"><a class="menu__link menu__link--sublist menu__link--sublist-caret" aria-expanded="false" tabindex="0" href="/xiao_esp32c6_getting_started/">XIAO ESP32C6</a></div></li><li class="theme-doc-sidebar-item-category theme-doc-sidebar-item-category-level-2 menu__list-item"><div class="menu__list-item-collapsible"><a class="menu__link menu__link--sublist menu__link--sublist-caret menu__link--active" aria-expanded="true" tabindex="0" href="/xiao_esp32s3_getting_started/">XIAO ESP32S3 (Sense)</a></div><ul style="display:block;overflow:visible;height:auto" class="menu__list"><li class="theme-doc-sidebar-item-link theme-doc-sidebar-item-link-level-3 menu__list-item"><a class="menu__link menu__link--active" aria-current="page" tabindex="0" href="/xiao_esp32s3_getting_started/">Getting Started with Seeed Studio XIAO ESP32S3 (Sense)</a></li><li class="theme-doc-sidebar-item-link theme-doc-sidebar-item-link-level-3 menu__list-item"><a class="menu__link" tabindex="0" href="/xiao_esp32s3_pin_multiplexing/">Pin Multiplexing with Seeed Studio XIAO ESP32S3 (Sense)</a></li><li class="theme-doc-sidebar-item-link theme-doc-sidebar-item-link-level-3 menu__list-item"><a class="menu__link" tabindex="0" href="/XIAO-ESP3253-Zephyr-RTOS/">XIAO ESP32S3(sense) With Zephyr(RTOS)</a></li><li class="theme-doc-sidebar-item-link theme-doc-sidebar-item-link-level-3 menu__list-item"><a class="menu__link" tabindex="0" href="/XIAO_ESP32S3_CircuitPython/">CircuitPython for ESP32S3</a></li><li 