color:#F8F8F2"><span class="token comment" style="color:rgb(98, 114, 164)">=====================================</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#F8F8F2"><span class="token comment" style="color:rgb(98, 114, 164)">This code is under Public Domain License.</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#F8F8F2"><span class="token comment" style="display:inline-block;color:rgb(98, 114, 164)"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#F8F8F2"><span class="token comment" style="color:rgb(98, 114, 164)">Author:</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#F8F8F2"><span class="token comment" style="color:rgb(98, 114, 164)">Pranav Cherukupalli &lt;<a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="b9dad1dccbccd2ccc9d8d5d5d0c9f9ded4d8d0d597dad6d4">[email&#160;protected]</a>&gt;</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#F8F8F2"><span class="token comment" style="color:rgb(98, 114, 164)">*/</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#F8F8F2"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#F8F8F2"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token macro property directive-hash">#</span><span class="token macro property directive keyword" style="color:rgb(189, 147, 249);font-style:italic">define</span><span class="token macro property"> </span><span class="token macro property macro-name">uS_TO_S_FACTOR</span><span class="token macro property"> </span><span class="token macro property expression number">1000000ULL</span><span class="token macro property expression">  </span><span class="token macro property comment" style="color:rgb(98, 114, 164)">/* Conversion factor for micro seconds to seconds */</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#F8F8F2"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token macro property directive-hash">#</